snippet: The United States takes on Jamaica in a World Cup qualifier without Landon Donovan or Michael Bradley and with Clint Dempsey rejoining the team days after a Premier League transfer.
lead_paragraph: The United States takes on Jamaica in a World Cup qualifier without Landon Donovan or Michael Bradley and with Clint Dempsey rejoining the team days after a Premier League transfer.
